---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Soluciones Corporate | Casa L&G Prestige">
  <main class="bg-[#0b0707] text-white min-h-screen">
    
    <section class="relative min-h-[85vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden px-6 pt-24">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
         <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,rgba(0,0,0,0.8)_0%,rgba(0,0,0,0.4)_100%)] z-10"></div>
         <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[40%] h-full bg-[#C5A059] opacity-[0.02] skew-x-[-20deg]"></div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="relative z-20 text-center md:text-left max-w-7xl mx-auto w-full grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="animate-slide-up">
            <p class="font-sans text-[#C5A059] tracking-[0.8em] text-[11px] uppercase mb-6">
                Executive & Business Line
            </p>
            <h1 class="font-premium text-5xl md:text-8xl text-white mb-8 tracking-tighter leading-[0.9]">
              DISTINCIÓN <br/>
              <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-[#F2D184] to-[#C5A059]">
                CORPORATIVA
              </span>
            </h1>
            <p class="font-sans text-white/60 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-xl mb-12 font-light">
              Elevamos la identidad de su institución a través de detalles que proyectan éxito y gratitud. La excelencia de Casa L&G al servicio de su empresa.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-6 justify-center md:justify-start">
                <a href="#divisiones" class="px-10 py-4 bg-white text-black font-sans font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[11px] hover:bg-[#C5A059] hover:text-white transition-all">Ver Divisiones</a>
                <a href="https://wa.me/51953435738" class="px-10 py-4 border border-white/20 text-white font-sans font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[11px] hover:border-[#C5A059] hover:text-[#C5A059] transition-all">Consultor B2B</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hidden md:flex justify-end opacity-20 md:opacity-100">
             <div class="relative w-80 h-[500px] border border-[#C5A059]/30 p-4">
                 <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-12 h-12 border-t-2 border-l-2 border-[#C5A059]"></div>
                 <div class="w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-br from-white/5 to-transparent flex items-center justify-center italic font-premium text-6xl text-[#C5A059]/10 select-none">
                    L&G
                 </div>
                 <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-12 h-12 border-b-2 border-r-2 border-[#C5A059]"></div>
             </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="divisiones" class="py-32 px-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-20">
        <h2 class="font-premium text-4xl md:text-6xl mb-4">Nuestras Divisiones</h2>
        <div class="h-[1px] w-24 bg-[#C5A059] mx-auto opacity-50"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        
        <div class="group bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-500 hover:bg-white/[0.04]">
          <div class="p-12 text-center">
            <span class="text-[#C5A059] font-sans text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-4 block">Line 01</span>
            <h3 class="font-premium text-3xl mb-6">Esencial</h3>
            <p class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-10">Detalles sobrios y elegantes. Diseñados para colaboradores y clientes frecuentes que valoran la distinción constante.</p>
            <div class="pt-8 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-col gap-3 text-left">
                <span class="text-[10px] uppercase text-white/60"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-[#C5A059] mr-2"></i> Elegancia Minimalista</span>
                <span class="text-[10px] uppercase text-white/60"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-[#C5A059] mr-2"></i> Branding Institucional</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group bg-white/[0.02] border-x-0 lg:border-x border-y border-white/10 lg:border-[#C5A059]/20 relative overflow-hidden transition-all duration-500 hover:bg-white/[0.05]">
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-[#C5A059]"></div>
          <div class="p-12 text-center">
            <span class="text-[#C5A059] font-sans text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-4 block">Line 02</span>
            <h3 class="font-premium text-3xl mb-6">Ejecutivo</h3>
            <p class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-10">Regalos Premium de alta gama. Pensados para Gerencias, socios estratégicos y cuentas clave que exigen excelencia.</p>
            <div class="pt-8 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-col gap-3 text-left">
                <span class="text-[10px] uppercase text-white/60"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-[#C5A059] mr-2"></i> Materiales Nobles</span>
                <span class="text-[10px] uppercase text-white/60"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-[#C5A059] mr-2"></i> Personalización de Autor</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-500 hover:bg-white/[0.04]">
          <div class="p-12 text-center">
            <span class="text-[#C5A059] font-sans text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-4 block">Line 03</span>
            <h3 class="font-premium text-3xl mb-6">Prestige</h3>
            <p class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-10">Experiencias empresariales exclusivas. Soluciones a medida para hitos institucionales y eventos de gala.</p>
            <div class="pt-8 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-col gap-3 text-left">
                <span class="text-[10px] uppercase text-white/60"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-[#C5A059] mr-2"></i> Eventos Personalizados</span>
                <span class="text-[10px] uppercase text-white/60"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-[#C5A059] mr-2"></i> Logística Guante Blanco</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-white/[0.01] py-32 border-y border-white/5">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-12">
                <div class="text-center group">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 border border-[#C5A059]/20 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:bg-[#C5A059] transition-all">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-stamp text-xl group-hover:text-black"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="font-premium text-sm tracking-widest uppercase">Marca Propia</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center group">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 border border-[#C5A059]/20 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:bg-[#C5A059] transition-all">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-box-archive text-xl group-hover:text-black"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="font-premium text-sm tracking-widest uppercase">Cajas Especiales</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center group">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 border border-[#C5A059]/20 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:bg-[#C5A059] transition-all">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-building-columns text-xl group-hover:text-black"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="font-premium text-sm tracking-widest uppercase">Regalos Institucionales</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center group">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 border border-[#C5A059]/20 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:bg-[#C5A059] transition-all">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-handshake-simple text-xl group-hover:text-black"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="font-premium text-sm tracking-widest uppercase">Eventos VIP</h4>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-32 px-6 text-center">
        <h2 class="font-premium text-3xl md:text-5xl mb-12">Impulse su Presencia Empresarial</h2>
        <a href="https://wa.me/51953435738" target="_blank" class="inline-block px-16 py-6 bg-transparent border-2 border-[#C5A059] text-[#C5A059] font-sans font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.4em] transition-all hover:bg-[#C5A059] hover:text-black shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(197,160,89,0.1)]">
            Solicitar Dossier Corporate
        </a>
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  @keyframes slide-up {
    from { transform: translateY(50px); opacity: 0; }
    to { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; }
  }
  .animate-slide-up { animation: slide-up 1s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) forwards; }
  .font-premium { font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; }
</style>